<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCAFFFEFC9B58515E65FFE5" blockId="39.[806,1029,54,115]" box="[807,1028,88,113]" pageId="39" pageNumber="591">Species Accounts</paragraph>
<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFCAFFFEFF7C5DC75EEBF983" pageId="39" pageNumber="591" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCAFFFEFF7C5DC75EEBF983" blockId="39.[190,1402,699,2346]" pageId="39" pageNumber="591">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFCAFFFEFF7C5DC75B4EFA7B" bold="true" box="[192,303,1486,1519]" pageId="39" pageNumber="591">Habitat.</emphasis>
Endemic in montane primary and secondary rainforests of the Sierra Nevada de Santa Marta, north-eastern Colombia at elevations of 680-2000 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFCAFFFEFF7C5E14588DF9F0" pageId="39" pageNumber="591" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFCAFFFEFF7C5E14588DF9F0" blockId="39.[190,1402,699,2346]" pageId="39" pageNumber="591">
